Package meka.gui.core

Class SearchParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • meka.gui.core.SearchParameters

  • public class SearchParameters
extends Object
    A container for search parameters.

    In case of simple substring matching, the search string and the string being searched are both used in lower case.
    Version:
    $Revision: 10824 $
    Author:
    fracpete (fracpete at waikato dot ac dot nz)
